{"tid":1176082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大蛇誤闖私家車　「屈蛇」死氣喉通街走","createTime":"2019-05-29T03:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T03:31:21.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca8d05a05ba225a4aa6303b38be90230e0e3669","tid":1176082,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T03:30:47.000Z","msg":"身為駕駛者，不時聽聞小貓會闖入車內引擎取暖，不過如果你座駕出現的不速之客是一條蟒蛇，你又會如何處理？日前有網民發布一段片段，一條疑似蟒蛇匿藏在一架正行駛私家車的死氣喉上，但司機卻懵然不知，不少網民都為司機抹一額汗，擔心其安危外，更責怪目擊者只顧拍片，沒有通知對方。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190528/photo/bkn-20190528131235205-0528_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190528153223\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190528%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190528131235205-0528_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190528153223&h=51b17432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190528/mobile/bkn-20190528131235205-0528_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190528%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190528131235205-0528_00822_001.html&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1Lq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=65430105\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190528/mobile/bkn-20190528131235205-0528_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"48dea7290a83d058c42f710398f12f69bdb31f55","tid":1176082,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T03:31:21.000Z","msg":"網民 Chun Ting Louie 昨日(28日)在Facebook群組「馬路的事討論區」上載一條片段，片段中可以看見一架私家車停在燈位前，車尾死氣喉被一條疑似蟒蛇纏住，而且不停在扭動打轉。目擊司機在貼文中謂，「有一秒想趁燈位落車提你，但我驚畀佢咬」、「轉燈後又追你唔到」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/833142083471222/permalink/2339600499492032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F833142083471222%2Fpermalink%2F2339600499492032&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1Lq%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=539911fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/833142083471222/permalink/2339600499492032</a>"}]}